														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1353563">
									

<p>I'm really not digging the latest addition (the viscous blue fluid in the water supply one). Too much is expunged; as it is, this sounds like the fluid or water supply would be classified as an SCP. Now, if the effect was that they started laughing uncontrollably for 30 minutes and some people with pre-existing breathing conditions managed to laugh so hard they choked/suffocated themselves to death, and it was explicitly a one-time thing (re-exposure to the fluid did nothing), then it might be interesting. As it is, it's too much generic [DATA EXPUNGED] with a [REDACTED] but not a mime, then [REMOVED BY ORDER OF O5-13] until golden-brown, and serve.</p>

							</div>

										<div class="signature">
					<hr class="signature-separator"/>
					

<p>Giving bearhugs to the unsuspecting since 1872.</p>

